<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TNT8">
<l>nīrakattāy neṭuvaraiyi ṉucci mēlāy</l>
<l>nilāttiṅkaḷ tuṇṭattāy niṟainta kacci</l>
<l>ūrakattā yoṇtuṟainīr veḵkā vuḷḷā</l>
<l>yuḷḷuvā ruḷḷattāy ulaka mēttum</l>
<l>kārakattāy kārvāṉat tuḷḷāy kaḷvā</l>
<l>kāmarupūṅ kāviriyiṉ teṉpāl maṉṉu</l>
<l>pērakattāy pērāteṉ neñci ṉuḷḷāy</l>
<l>perumāṉuṉ tiruvaṭiyē pēṇi ṉēṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>You of Nīrakam, you who is on the peak of a high mountain,</l>
<l rend="indent">of Nilāttinkaḷtuṇṭam, and of Ūrakam in prosperous Kacci,</l>
<l>You who is in Veḵkā with glittering harbor waters,</l>
<l rend="indent">you in the hearts of those who think [of you],</l>
<l>You of Kārakam, which the world praises, in Kārvāṉam, O thief,</l>
<l rend="indent">you within Pēr established on the south side of the lush, desirable Kāviri,</l>
<l>You  who is  in my heart without leaving,</l>
<l rend="indent">Great Lord, [in all of these] I cherished your divine feet.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
